{"tid":355934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚險車禍】途人捱撞倒地 排檔女職員：佢下半身郁唔到","createTime":"2017-08-11T16:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T04:52:19.000Z","uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"361b903d1b9992d0f737afed73547cb8f68ce6f4","tid":355934,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"【驚險車禍】途人捱撞倒地 排檔女職員：佢下半身郁唔到<br />\n<br />\n貨車在中環鴨巴甸街衝落斜，撼向店舖外牆始停下。附近衣服檔職員張小姐形容，當時聽到一聲巨響，「初時仲以為冧棚，之後見到架貨車車尾，先知係撞車！」她續指：「有個途人被撞倒瞓咗喺地上，好痛，佢下半身郁唔到，貨車司機亦夾喺車上，伸手求救。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，事發現場1米之隔、險被貨車直撞入舖的一間首飾店，店東朱先生事後猶有餘悸，指事發時其太太在店內看舖，貨車突然衝到店外，幸有路邊防撞欄阻擋，否則恐撞入店內。他形容之前還想拆走店外「土地公公」，幸「有土地公公保祐」，又指太太在事件中「嚇親」，惟有驚無險，已回家休息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170811/large/1502457527_f611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170811%2Flarge%2F1502457527_f611.jpg&h=1a2b2f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附近衣服檔職員張小姐指男途人被撞傷倒地，「下半身郁唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170811/57070592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170811%2F57070592&d=Xt7tVUxxvNt2P1f2yomdudibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=24ee0b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170811%2F57070592&h=a1adeaa9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170811/57070592</a>"},{"pid":"78a391a5df871673d80081ca6e513c91e87a99fc","tid":355934,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"佢郁唔到,咪你郁law<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係話報警求助"},{"pid":"ce752d79bdb76fb63a9b32ec44c9